translations: n.[通信]中继器（repeater 的复数）

phrs.translation: 中继器, 红石中继器, 连发枪

sentences.sentence: The course indication of Repeaters does not match that of gyro compass.
sentences.translation: 主罗经和分罗经航向示度不匹配。

sentences.sentence: The repeaters on the list, for their part, have done plenty of good work over the past year.
sentences.translation: 榜单上再次出现的慈善家，在过去一年里在慈善方面都做出了巨大努力。

sentences.sentence: After becoming bored with Repeaters and HTs, I decided to make one last attempt to master the code.
sentences.translation: 在成为与中继器和高温超导无聊，我决定做最后一次努力掌握代码。
